IRemoteTaskViewAdapter - Interface in provided.compute
A remote view adapter that enables a task or any other part of a system to display a text message on the user interface of a remote system.
This adapter IS an RMI Server object! Instantiations of this interface should NEVER be sent to a remote machine, only STUBs made from this Remote object should ever be transmitted.
